<div class="col-sm-12 tournament-header" style="">
    <h1 class="t-heading">Money Match Gaming Rules</h1>
</div>
<div class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2" style="padding:30px;margin-top:50px;">
    <div><img class="imgDiv1" src="/Images/leftupperpane.png" /></div>
    <div class="contentDiv" style="width:100%;">
        <div style="position: absolute;top: -10px;left: 55px;"><h3>Basic Guidelines</h3></div>
        <div>
            <ol>
                <li>
                    <span>All users are responsible for checking the rules in his/her own time, as they are always subject to change without notice.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>All services are provided as is, and are subject to change.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>All users must be 13 or older. Users found to be breaking this rule will be banned.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>No piracy discussion or links to sites that advocate piracy. No exceptions will be made.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>Cheating and lying to bypass the established rules of play is prohibited. Getting caught cheating or lying about the outcome of matches during ranked games will receive a punishment equal to the offense. Helping people boost through the ranks, playing off site outside of our format and purposefully sandbagging in ranked matches are examples of cheating.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>Be respectful of all users on the site. Inappropriate conduct such as flaming, harassing and demoralizing language is not tolerated. Users breaking this rule will find their privileges revoked, such as display names.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>No linking of explicit content such as borderline nudity, suggestive themes and full blown pornography</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>Moderators are here to keep the peace and impeding their ability to do so through harassment or otherwise will result in punishment. Privately contact a moderator concerning an issue you have with the site.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>Inappropriate names including (but not limited to): sexual, drug, explicit, or racial language are not allowed.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>Unless given permission by the other party, posting private or match chat logs is not allowed.</span>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>

    </div>

</div>

<div class="col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2" style="padding:30px;margin-top:50px;">
