                <li>
                    <span>Latency/Lag may not be optimal when playing people across the country.  Users should try to be fair and understand the circumstances and play their best regardless of the conditions.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>Complaints about playability should be brought up to the tournament organizer before a match has been completed.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
